You probably thought I forgot about this video… but I didn’t! Just school, work, and a little laziness 🫣
But here it is, even though literally everyone has already tried these dates, you still get to hear my take.

And for those who don’t know: they taste exactly like candy but with zero added sugar = win-win for those of us trying to cut cut down on sugar like me 🍬
Did any flavor catch your eye?

P.S. Not a collab, just hopped on the trend and wanted to try something a bit different 🙃
